agi-safety-brakes-for-neural-and-symbolic-systems</guid></item><item><title>科技巨头为了延长寿命而对自己的身体进行黑客攻击：他们的方法背后有科学依据吗？</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/tech-titans-are-hacking-their-bodies-for-a-longer-life-is-there-science-behind-their-methods</link><description>希望延长寿命的影响者和超级富豪正在交流如何维持额外寿命的技巧和窍门。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/tech-titans-are-hacking-their-bodies-for-a-longer-life-is-there-science-behind-their-methods2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jun 2026 01:09:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/tech-titans-are-hacking-their-bodies-for-a-longer-life-is-there-science-behind-their-methods</guid></item><item><title>自主医疗人工智能在模拟 EHR 病例中的表现优于医生</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/autonomous-medical-ai-outperforms-doctors-in-simulated-ehr-cases</link><description>MIRA 是一种在沙盒电子健康记录中进行测试的自主 AI 代理，它诊断了 574 例真实的急诊科病例，准确率达 88.9%，并且在 311 例匹配的比较中表现优于医生。该系统在模拟中下令进行测试、生成药物计划并做出入院决定，但作者强调，前瞻性验证、治理和医生监督仍然至关重要。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/autonomous-medical-ai-outperforms-doctors-in-simulated-ehr-cases2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jun 2026 16:25:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/autonomous-medical-ai-outperforms-doctors-in-simulated-ehr-cases</guid></item><item><title>光控微夹具弥合了精度和力量之间的差距</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/light-controlled-microgripper-bridges-the-gap-between-precision-and-force</link><description>一段时间以来，研究人员使用光镊通过精心控制的激光束以令人难以置信的精度操纵微小物体。然而到目前为止，这种技术对其所能施加的力量始终有严格的限制。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/light-controlled-microgripper-bridges-the-gap-between-precision-and-force2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jun 2026 16:10:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/light-controlled-microgripper-bridges-the-gap-between-precision-and-force</guid></item><item><title>泛癌神经递质受体改变定义了具有预后意义的神经调节亚型</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/pan-cancer-neurotransmitter-receptor-alterations-define-neuroregulatory-subtypes-with-prognostic-significance</link><description>罗等人。使用来自癌症基因组图谱和其他独立队列的多维组学数据，对 33 种癌症类型的神经递质受体基因进行全面的分子描绘。他们确定了具有独特分子特征的临床相关神经调节亚型，推动了癌症神经科学的新兴领域。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/pan-cancer-neurotransmitter-receptor-alterations-define-neuroregulatory-subtypes-with-prognostic-significance2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jun 2026 15:55:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/pan-cancer-neurotransmitter-receptor-alterations-define-neuroregulatory-subtypes-with-prognostic-significance</guid></item><item><title>特雷西·R·阿特金斯 (Tracy R. Atkins) 谈 Aeternum Ray：不要等待奇点</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/tracy-r-atkins-on-aeternum-ray-dont-wait-for-the-singularity</link><description>&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/tracy-r-atkins-on-aeternum-ray-dont-wait-for-the-singularity.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jun 2026 15:40:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/tracy-r-atkins-on-aeternum-ray-dont-wait-for-the-singularity</guid></item><item><title>红色火星变绿色——给地球带来一点地球化改造的感觉</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/red-mars-to-green-giving-the-planet-a-touch-of-terraforming</link><description>科罗拉多州戈尔登——科学家们正在进行研究，希望在未来将火星的寒冷气候转变为对地球人来说更加人性化的地方。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/red-mars-to-green-giving-the-planet-a-touch-of-terraforming2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jun 2026 15:25:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/red-mars-to-green-giving-the-planet-a-touch-of-terraforming</guid></item></channel></rss>